issue.title: Selecting photos to details flow
issue.body:
1) When you click "Get help" on the photos page, you should be able to select a subset of photos to "chat" about
2) Once you have selected these photos, you click "Get Help"
3) Redirect to the details page
4) On the details page, view each picture individually (ideally in something like a photo carousel) and only see the comments of the photo that you are looking at
